This paper discusses the evaluation procedures of the Italian research system, specifically in the context of scientometrics. It also touches on the failure of knowledge transfer from R&D to engineering and production. These topics are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
